{
  "name": "Full Meeting Summary",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an executive assistant analyzing meeting notes.\n\nMeeting notes:\n{{ $json.content.parts[0].text }}{{ $json.Text_1 }}\n\nTasks:\nAnalyze these meeting notes and extract relevant information based on context.\n\nGUIDELINES:\n1. If meeting discusses TASKS/ASSIGNMENTS:\n   - Extract action items with task, assignee (if any), due date (if any)\n   - If assignee not mentioned, use \"Unassigned\"\n   - If due date not mentioned, use null\n\n2. If meeting is INFORMATIVE/UPDATE:\n   - Focus on: main topic, decisions made, milestone/key dates\n   - Create a brief summary\n\n3. If meeting is DISCUSSION/IDEATION:\n   - Focus on: main ideas, key discussion points, conclusions\n\n4. If meeting is COORDINATION:\n   - Focus on: coordinator, timeline, dependencies, blockers\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (JSON):\n{\n  \"meeting_type\": \"task | informative | discussion | coordination\",\n  \"meeting_topic\": \"string (short meeting title)\",\n  \"meeting_date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD or null if not mentioned\",\n  \"summary\": \"string (1-2 sentence brief summary)\",\n  \"key_points\": [\"point 1\", \"point 2\", ...],\n  \"decisions\": [\"decision 1\", \"decision 2\", ...] (if any),\n  \"action_items\": [\n    {\n      \"task\": \"string\",\n      \"assignee\": \"string\",\n      \"due_date\": \"string or null\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"next_steps\": \"string (optional)\"\n}\n\nRULES:\n- Do not use ``` in output\n- If no action items, leave action_items array empty []\n- Adjust fields based on meeting type (fields may be null if not relevant)\n- Use English for all output text\n\nIF TEXT IS NOT RELATED TO A MEETING, RESPOND WITH \"NULL\"",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        656,
        208
      ],
      "id": "YOUR_NODE_ID_HERE",
      "name": "AI Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "llama-3.3-70b-versatile",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGroq",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        656,
        400
      ],
      "id": "YOUR_NODE_ID_HERE",
      "name": "Groq Chat Model",
      "credentials": {
        "groqApi": {
          "id": "YOUR_CREDENTIAL_ID_HERE",
          "name": "Groq account"
        }
      }
